BARD PATTERNS

Bards can discover hidden harmonies by playing song forms in the right order.
Some song fields can also pivot into deeper patterns when the room, party,
instrument, archetype, or enemy state is right.

When you discover either kind of pattern, your Bard soul records it.

Useful commands:

  bpatterns              Show every pattern you have learned.
  bpatterns harmonies    Show only hidden harmonies.
  bpatterns pivots       Show only song-field pivots.
  bpatterns <name>       Show one learned pattern by name.

Aliases:

  bharmonies
  bdiscoveries

The list shows the sequence or condition that triggered the pattern, plus how
many times you have seen it. Discoveries are saved with your Bard soul and
remain available after relogging.

